<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFF0FFEEE38B0230FC2FFD46" author="Higgins, L. G." box="[689,908,618,645]" pageId="8" pageNumber="33" pagination="175 - 365" refId="ref9372" refString="Higgins, L. G. (1941) An illustrated catalogue of the Palearctic Melitaea (Lep. Rhopalocera). Transactions of the Royal Entomological Society of London, 91, 175 - 365. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1365 - 2311.1941. tb 01045. x" type="journal article" year="1941">Higgins 1941: 166</bibRefCitation>
